@startuml m6-declarative-spec-compiler-sequence
skinparam dpi 300
title M6 — One Declarative FT Spec -> OTP + K8s

participant "Developer" as DEV
participant "FT spec (DSL)" as SPEC
participant "Compiler" as C
participant "OTP supervision\n(generated)" as OTP
participant "K8s manifests\n(generated)" as K8S

DEV -> SPEC: declare intent\n(statefulness, recovery, quorum, timing)
SPEC -> C: compile
C -> OTP: supervisor tree + strategy\n+ max_restarts + shutdown
C -> K8S: probes + PDB + grace\n+ anti-affinity
note over OTP,K8S #ccffcc: both layers consistent\nby construction (no config drift)
@enduml
